item.title: Autofighters
item.dc:creator: @KyleGut3 KyleGut3
item.description:
@KyleGut3 wrote:

it might not necessarily be the script thats slow, it could be your computer that cant handle the contant flow of coding going through scar [unlikely, but possible].

If you want a basic fighter, you could probably make one yourself using simple include knowledge and how to color-pick.

as to going to aryan, i dont suggest it if that character you want to use has any value to you. and if it does not, i suggest using iamadam’s chicken killer script [which you can change during startup to cowsi believe]
